Example that tests MPI persistent send/receive messages using NVIDIA GPU-direct.

Adapted from
http://www.llnl.gov/computing/tutorials/mpi_performance/samples/persist.c
by Ned Nedialkov
Department of Computing and SoftwareMcMaster University, Hamilton, Ontario, Canada

To test on DOE Sierra machine:
lrun -n2 ./test
lrun -M "-gpu" -n2 ./test_omp
